         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Lampadios to my lord brother Apollonios, greeting. Since you do not want to do us a favour at your expence, I paid in Thmoinepsobthis 35 artabae (of ?). But also my brother Skybalos paid 24 ........ many ambiguous (?);Verso:;To my lord brother Apollonios.</ab>
